<seg id=1> China will speed up the talented person market system construction </seg>
</hl> 
<p> 
<seg id=2> The New China News Agency Beijing on September first the news Central Committee of the CCP organization department, the human resources department recently sent out the notice, the request strengthens the talented person market construction plan, sped up the talented person market development step, promoted the talented person market health development. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=3> The notice points out, cultivates and develops the talented person market overall goal is: Realizes individual independently select industry, the unit independently selects the person, the market adjustment supply and demand, the social service is perfect, the society safeguards perfectly, under the national macroscopic regulation, causes the market to play the foundation role in the talented person resources disposition aspect. </seg>
<seg id=4> Will cultivate and develops the talented person market short-term goal is: Formulates the basic policy laws and regulations within the nearly 23 years which the talented person market movement needs, generally establishes the talented person market place in the major and medium city, establishes and develops the local talented person information network, supports the specialized talented person market development, the establishment regional talented person market. </seg>
<seg id=5> Before 2000, initially completes the function in the national scope consummates, the mechanism is perfect necessary, the laws and regulations, the instruction is prompt, the service thorough talented person market system. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=6> Center the group, the human resources department requests all levels of organization human affairs department to strengthen the talented person market construction and the management, strengthens the talented person market the research and the plan, establishes the talented person market development the overall layout and the implementation step, acts as circumstances permit, the classified instruction, gradually establishes the consummation the talented person market system. </seg>
</p> 
